U7 chit8 e5 a-peh, i ka-ki7 tiam3 ti7 soaN-piN e5 chit8 keng bo5 chin toa7 e5 chhu3, i u7 chin-choe7 e5 iuN5-a2, tak8 jit8 i tioh8 chhoa7 hiah e5 iuN5-a2 chhut-lai5 chiah8 chhau2.
Chin tu2-ho2 u7 chit8 keng hak8-hau7 ti7 soaN-teng2, ia7 tak8 jit8 long2 u7 gin2-na2 tui3 chit e5 a-peh teh chhi7 iuN5 e5 sou2-chai7 ke3-khi3.  Na7 kap a-peh saN-kiN3 e5 si5, a-peh long2 chin ho2, ka7 in kio3, u7 si5 ka7 in kong2, lin2 na7 thak8-chheh tng2-lai5, goa2 chiah kong2 kou3-su7 hou7 lin2 thiaN, gin2-na2 ia7 u7 si5 oe7 kong2 hak8-hau7 e5 lau7-su kap in e5 peng5-iu2 hou7 a-peh thiaN, tui3 an2-ni, u7 chin-choe7 e5 gin2-na2 kap a-peh choe3 ho2 e5 peng5-iu2.
U7 chit8 jit8, chiah e5 gin2-na2 long2 chin hoaN-hi2 tui3 hak8-hau7 tng2-lai5, kau3 a-peh teh chhi7 iuN5 e5 sou2-chai7, a-peh, li2 kiam2 chai bin5-a2-chai3 si7 sim2-mih8 jit8?  A-peh kong2, “Si7 Kam2-sia7-choeh.” 
“Tioh8.” “Goan2 lau7-su kio3 goan2 long2 theh8 chit8 hang7 goan2 sou2 choe3 e5, a2-si7 goan2 chhi7 e5 mih8 khi3 hian3 neh!”  
U7 chit8 e5 kong2, “Goa2 beh ban2 goa2 sou2 cheng3 e5 hoe;” koh chit8 e5 kong2, “Goa2 beh hian3 chit8 chiah thou3-a2;” koh chit8 e5 kong2, “Goa2 beh hian3 hoan-beh8!”  “Goa2 beh hian3 kam-a2-bit8.” “Goa2 beh hian3 kam-a2.”  
A-peh chiu7 kong2, “Lin2 long2 chin koai, tak8 e5 long2 chin jin7-chin teh choe3 kang, goa2 sit8-chai7 chin ai3 khi3 chham-ka lin2 e5 kam2-sia7 le2-pai3.”  
Hiah e5 gin2-na2 chiu7 kong2, “A-peh, li2 bin5-a2-chai3 tioh8 lai5 chham-ka goan2 e5 hoaN-hi2, it-teng7 tioh8 lai5 lah houN3?  A-peh!”  A-peh kong2, “ho2.”
Keh jit8, tak8 e5 gin2-na2 long2 chin hoaN-hi2, chheng7 chin cheng2-choe5 beh khi3 hak8-hau7, keng-ke3 chhau2-tiuN5, bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 a-peh, long2 siuN7 kong2 a-peh tai7-khai3 teh chun2-pi7 beh khi3 hu3 in e5 kam2-sia7-choeh!  Chiu7 long2 theh8 in beh hian3 e5 mih8 kau3 hak8-hau7.  Bo5 joa7-ku2, lau7-su kong2 lai5 khai-si2 kam2-sia7 le2-pai3, saN-kap gim5-si, koh ki5-to2, au7-lai5 tai7-ke long2 ban7-ban7 theh8 in tui3 Siong7-te3 hia sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 mih8 chhut-khi3 pai5 ti7 thau5-cheng5 e5 toh-teng2.  
Lau7-su tioh8 ka7 hiah e5 hak8-seng kong2 khi2 kam2-sia7-choeh si7 tui3 1620 ni5, u7 chin-choe7 Ki-tok-tou5 tui3 Eng-kok cho7 chit8 chiah chun5, beh chhe7 chit8 e5 sou2-chai7 ti7 hia lai5 keng3-pai3 Siong7-te3; chong2-si7 chit chiah chun5 bo5 phah-sng3 ti7 poaN3-lou7 tu2-tioh8 hong-eng2, soa3 theng5 ti7 chit8 e5 sin e5 tai7-liok8, ti7 hit si5 tu2 si7 12 geh8 thiN chin koaN5, mih8-kiaN7 i2-keng chiah8 beh liau2, ti3-kau3 u7 e5 soa3 iau kap koaN5 si2, sit8-chai7 u7 tu2-tioh8 choe7-choe7 e5 kan-khou2.  
Chong2-si7 in ia7 chit8 bin7 phah-piaN3 choe3 kang, u7 e5 kut8 chhan5-hng5, u7 e5 chhi7 cheng-siN, chit8 ni5 ku2 e5 phah-piaN3, koh tit-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 pang-chan7, in beh eng7 e5 mih8-kiaN7 chiam7-chiam7 u7 kau3, in ia7 long2 bo5 boe7 ki3-tit Siong7-te3, in tak8 e5 chiu7 chu7-chip8 khi2-lai5, hoaN-hoaN hi2-hi2 o-lo2 ThiN-pe7 chhoa7 in keng-ke3 chin kan-khou2 e5 chit8 ni5 ku2, che si7 kam2-sia7-choeh e5 thau5 chit8 pai2.  
Hiah e5 gin2-na2 thiaN liau2, lan2 ma7 tioh8 oe7 hiau2-tit kam2-sia7, in-ui7 Siong7-te3 ia7 chin thiaN3 lan2, in tioh8 koh gim5-si o-lo2 ThiN-pe7.  Kau3 le2-pai3 soah, lau7-su chiu7 kong2, kin-a2-jit8 lan2 hian3 chiah e5 mih8 long2 beh theh8 lai5 pang-chan7 khah kan-khou2 e5 lang5, lin2 m7-chai chai u7 sim2-mih8 lang5 bo5?
Hiah e5 gin2-na2 oat8-lai5 oat8-khi3, teh siuN7 kong2, lan2 u7 chhiaN2 a-peh lai5, thai2 oe7 long2 bo5 lai5 leh?  It-teng7 si7 teh kan-khou2, i tak8 jit8 hiah phah-piaN3 choe3 kang, koh i2-keng hiah lau7, sit8-chai7 chin kho2-lin5.  
Ti7 hit tiong-kan u7 chit8 e5 gin2-na2 chiu7 ka7 lau7-su kong2, “Lau7-su, goan2 u7 kap chit8 e5 a-peh chin ho2, i tak8 jit8 long2 ti7 soaN-kha hiah e5 chhau2-tiuN5 teh kou3 iuN5, goan2 cha-hng u7 kio3 i kin-a2-jit8 lai5 chham-ka lan2 e5 kam2-sia7 le2-pai3, i u7 ka7 goan2 kong2 ho2, chong2-si7 long2 bo5 lai5, goa2 siuN7, i un2-tang3 si7 teh phoa3-piN7, lau7-su, goa2 siuN7 tioh8 ai3 eng7 tam7-poh8 lan2 hian3 e5 mih8 lai5 pang-chan7 i, hoe a2-si7 ke2-chi2 long2 ho2.”
Lau7-su chiu7 kong2, “Chin ho2, lin2 long2 oe7 hiau2-tit beh pang-chan7 hiah e5 kan-khou2 e5 lang5, Siong7-te3 it-teng7 chin hoaN-hi2.”  U7 chin-choe7 e5 gin2-na2 chiu7 saN-kap khi3 tham3 hit e5 a-peh, ko2-jian5 u7 iaN2 a-peh si7 teh kan-khou2, to2 ti7 bin5-chhng5, i khoaN3 tioh8 hiah choe7 gin2-na2 lai5 chin hoaN-hi2, hiah e5 gin2-na2 gim5 chin ho2 thiaN e5 si hou7 a-peh thiaN, ia7 sang3 a-peh chin-choe7 le2-mih8, bo5 joa7-ku2 chiu7 ka7 a-peh chai3-chian2!
Hit-am3, a-peh ka-ki7 chit8 e5 che7 ti7 thang-a2 piN khoaN3 thiN, u7 choe7-choe7 e5 sio2 kim-chhiN, i chiu7 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, sui-jian5 i ka-ki7 chit8 e5, chong2-si7 i u7 kam2-kak Siong7-te3 kap i saN-kap ti7-teh!  Siong7-te3 m7-na7 hou7 hiah e5 gin2-na2 oe7 thiaN3 i, koh am3-si5 hou7 hiah-nih choe7 e5 sio2 kim-chhiN kap i choe3 phoaN7.
（Lu2-soan Geh8-khan Te7 71 ki5, 1965 ni5 11 geh8)
